title: Wipeout
description:
Written by Zack Phillips

Starring Avery Monsen, Dan Hodapp, Jonathan Marballi, Kelly Hudson, Langan Kingsley, James McCarthy, Kristy Lopez-Bernal.

Directed by John Flynn.

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, August 13, 2012.

Filmed by Alex Aden.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
